1.1.0 [2025-04-01]
- HEVC 10-bit encoding support (libx265, hevc_nvenc, hevc_vaapi)
- Bayer ordered dithering to reduce color banding in encoded output
- SSE2-accelerated dither path on x86-64

1.0.0 [2025-03-31]
Initial release:
- OpenGL framebuffer capture with PBO double-buffering
- FFmpeg H.264 encoding (libx264, h264_nvenc, h264_vaapi)
- SRT output via MPEG-TS (caller and listener modes)
- Async encoding on a separate thread with double-buffered frame handoff
- Non-blocking SRT connection with timeout and cancel support
- Automatic disconnect detection
- Toolbar button with SRT icon
- Qt configuration dialog with status indicator
- Keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Shift+S, Ctrl+Shift+R)
- Builds as static plugin (Windows + Linux) or dynamic plugin (Linux)
